# V1: RequestBackpackInventoryContentsPayload info leak — suggested fix

Require the requesting player to have an existing, legitimate reason to know that UUID. The simplest correct model is: the server maintains a per-player "seen backpacks" set, populated when the server opens a `BackpackContainer` menu for that player, and cleared on disconnect.

